def agent_action(execution_engine, member_id):
    if member_id >= len(execution_engine.current_members):
        return
    me = execution_engine.current_members[member_id]

    # Analyze who has attacked me
    victim_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict.get('victim', None)
    if victim_matrix is None or me.id >= victim_matrix.shape[0]:
        return

    attacks_against_me = victim_matrix[me.id]
    if not hasattr(attacks_against_me, 'tolist'):
        attacks_against_me = attacks_against_me.tolist()
    attackers = [(idx, count) for idx, count in enumerate(attacks_against_me) if count > 0 and idx != member_id]
    if attackers:
        # Sort attackers by number of attacks descending
        attackers.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)
        target_id = attackers[0][0]
        if target_id < len(execution_engine.current_members):
            target_member = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
            execution_engine.attack(me, target_member)
            return

    # If not attacked, offer help to the member with highest benefit received
    benefit_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict.get('benefit', None)
    if benefit_matrix is not None and me.id < benefit_matrix.shape[0]:
        benefits = benefit_matrix[me.id]
        if not hasattr(benefits, 'tolist'):
            benefits = benefits.tolist()
        beneficiaries = [(idx, value) for idx, value in enumerate(benefits) if idx != member_id]
        if beneficiaries:
            # Sort beneficiaries by benefit descending
            beneficiaries.sort(key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)
            target_id = beneficiaries[0][0]
            if target_id < len(execution_engine.current_members):
                target_member = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
                execution_engine.offer(me, target_member, True)
                return

    # As a last resort, check if any member has land to bear
    benefit_land_matrix = execution_engine.relationship_dict.get('benefit_land', None)
    if benefit_land_matrix is not None and me.id < benefit_land_matrix.shape[0]:
        lands = benefit_land_matrix[me.id]
        if not hasattr(lands, 'tolist'):
            lands = lands.tolist()
        land_bearers = [idx for idx, value in enumerate(lands) if value > 0 and idx != member_id]
        if land_bearers:
            target_id = land_bearers[0]
            if target_id < len(execution_engine.current_members):
                target_member = execution_engine.current_members[target_id]
                execution_engine.bear(me, target_member)
                return
